Win32/Wallpaper version 0.02
============================

The Win32::Wallpaper module allows you to modify the wallpaper, 
or background image, on your Win32 desktop. BitMaPs (BMPs) are 
the only images supported. 

You can set three wallpaper styles: center, stretch, and tile.  

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   nmake
   nmake test
   nmake install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

 Win32::API, Win32::TieRegistry, Win32::AbsPath, Image::Size

